---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="收到了" description="諮詢表單送出成功">
  <article class="max-w-xl mx-auto px-8 py-24 text-center">
    <div class="font-mono text-xs text-teal uppercase tracking-[.08em] mb-4">RECEIVED · OK</div>
    <h1 class="font-display text-ink leading-[1.02] tracking-[-0.03em] font-semibold"
        style="font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);">
      <span class="text-teal">謝謝</span>。
    </h1>
    <p class="font-display text-muted text-lg mt-6 leading-relaxed">
      我會在 1–2 個工作日內回信。如果適合進一步聊，會附上 Google Calendar 預約連結。
    </p>
    <a href="/" class="btn-ghost mt-8 inline-block">← 回首頁</a>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
